meta {
  name: 02 - get me unauthenticated
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/user
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Origin: {{spaOrigin}}
}

docs {
  # Negative: /api/user without any credential should 401.

  If you ran the SPA flow up to 04-logout, cookies are now invalid.
  If you ran only the bearer flow up to 03-revoke-token, no bearer is
  in scope. Either way the request must hit the auth:sanctum middleware
  and bounce with 401.

  To force a clean state in Bruno: open a new request tab, run this,
  confirm 401. Do NOT click "Run All" after the logout/revoke request
  to keep the failure deterministic.

  Expected: 401 Unauthorized.
}
